76561198009479784,Recommended,315460,29435968,Posted: 22 January,all,Vextris,"Dig or Die is a really fun base building, survival game in which you explore the world, collect materials and resources and craft various weapons and armor in addition to bases and base defenses to help you survive the night.  What makes this game special and sets it apart from other games in the genre is:1) Each night, you will be swarmed by the enemies you have killed at least once in your playthrough.2) The rain/water mechanics which add an amazing amount of depth to the game and should not be overlooked.3) The building physics of the blocks and how they support one another.  Very fun stuff!I really enjoyed playing through this game and have done so twice now.  I highly recommend it as long as you like base building, action/adventure, recourse gathering/crafting games as well as base defense games.  You can play it many different ways and are only truly limited by your own imagination.*This is an early access title but for only $7.99 USD, this game is worth the full price in my opinion.  I am not sure how much more support or additional development the developers plan to do to support this game as it seems very finished and complete as it is.  I had NO crashes or bugs with the two playthroughs I did."
