 world to explore, not small.9. The way you don't move in flowing water, that's just so unrealistic in a physics game.10. Some minerals are far too hard to find, it ruins the game having to look for hours to find an ore.There you go! If you wish me to go into detail about any of these or want me to purchase another game to test for you and give improvements, then email me atwinnerasyougo@gmail.comI look forward to seeing this game progress through early access and I hope you use my review to improve the game!I hope you find this review useful and/or wish to use it as feedback. Please get back in touch if you need anything!ConGsta15 -"
